node.text:
Spa GIVEAWAY 🧖‍♀️💦 To celebrate @AireAncientBaths_US launching their NEW digital e-gift immersive experience, we’re giving you a chance to win an experience for yourself AND gift two friends a customized digital box with a personalized message valid for the signature Ancient Thermal Bath Experience.
To Enter: 1. Tag your friends and 2. Follow @AireAncientBaths_US (For a bonus entry, enter your email at our link-in-bio!)
Check our link-in-bio for more details! #NYBucketlist #Partner -- Giveaway not affiliated with IG, value $800, will end on 11:59 EST 8/3. Selection details & terms: bit.ly/bucketlistterms

node.text:
A NEW way to experience Immersive Van Gogh - Tag a friend! 🧘‍♀️🌌 You can now take a 35-min yoga class inside this larger-than-life exhibit! Tickets to the following experiences are now available at Bucketlisters.com or our link-in-bio.
🧘‍♂️ Immersive Yoga Class
💕 Date Night Experience (Use Code 'FULL')
✨ General Admission Tickets

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by New York Bucket List in Manhattan, New York with @nybucketlist, and @coronausa. May be an image of ocean and text.

node.text:
Sailing GIVEAWAY 🍻⛵️☀️ To celebrate summer, @CoronaUSA is giving away the chance for you & 4 friends to spend a day on their Corona Sailboat (hint: you may have spotted it on the Hudson this month!) 
TO ENTER: Check the link in our bio – you’ll also find an epic list of our favorite happy hour spots in NYC 😉 #NYBucketlist #Partner 
—- No purchase necessary. Residents of NY (“Eligibility Area”) 21+. Ends 9/6/21. Void where prohibited. Rules: www.CoronaSummerbration.com

node.text: Treat yo’self - it’s #NationalIceCreamDay 🙌🍦 Find our round up of the 21 best ice cream shops in the U.S. (plus! a special ticket to the Museum of Ice Cream) at Bucketlisters.com or our link-in-bio! #NYBucketlist

node.text: Who wants to beat the heat with a FREE swirl?🍦☀️To celebrate #NationalIceCreamDay, @bookingcom has decked out a colorful ice cream truck to give out free ice cream in Union Square this Sunday from 1-2PM. With original ice cream flavors inspired by worldwide travel, this is also the first-ever ice cream truck that can host an overnight stay (Check our stories for an inside look!) #NYBucketlist
